
<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Pages — amisoeu</title>
  <style>
    :root{--bg:#0f1724;--card:#0b1220;--muted:#9aa4b2;--accent:#22c55e;--glass:rgba(255,255,255,0.04)}
    body{font-family:Inter,system-ui,Segoe UI,Roboto,"Helvetica Neue",Arial;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#071026 0%, #071020 60%),var(--bg);color:#e6eef6;margin:0;padding:40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh}
    .wrap{width:100%;max-width:900px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.02),transparent);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;box-shadow:0 6px 30px rgba(2,6,23,0.6);backdrop-filter:blur(6px)}
    header{display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:center}
    .avatar{width:84px;height:84px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0ea5a4,#22c55e);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:28px;color:#021018}
    h1{margin:0;font-size:28px}
    p.lead{color:var(--muted);margin:8px 0 18px}
    .contacts{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px}
    .chip{background:var(--glass);padding:8px 12px;border-radius:999px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}
    a.chip:hover{outline:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04)}
    section{margin-top:20px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;gap:20px}
    .main{background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.01),transparent);padding:18px;border-radius:10px}
    .side{background:var(--card);padding:18px;border-radius:10px;color:var(--muted)}
    h2{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:18px;color:#e6eef6}
    .projects{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
    .project-link{display:block;text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    .project{padding:12px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02);transition:transform .12s ease,box-shadow .12s ease}
    .project:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(2,6,23,0.6)}
    .project h3{margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#dff7e0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:10px}
    .project p{margin:6px 0 0;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px}
    .tags{margin-top:10px;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .tag{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);padding:6px 8px;border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
    footer{margin-top:18px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;text-align:center}
    .repo{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)}
    @media (max-width:800px){section{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap" role="main">
    <header>
      <div class="avatar">AM</div>
      <div>
        <h1>Привет! Я — amisoeu</h1>
        <p class="lead">Начинающий программист. Изучаю веб‑разработку и создаю первые проекты.</p>
        <div class="contacts">
          <a class="chip" href="https://t.me/amisoeu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Telegram: @amisoeu</a>
          <a class="chip" href="https://github.com/minelyeu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub: minelyeu</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <div class="main">
        <h2>Проекты</h2>
        <div class="projects">
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/NoLlyTre/Fitnes-bot-python" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <article class="project" id="fitnessbot">
              <h3>FitnessBot</h3>
              <p>Телеграм‑бот, который помогает в фитнесе: создаёт планы тренировок, считает подходы/повторы, напоминания о тренировках и отслеживает прогресс.</p>
              <div class="tags">
                <span class="tag">Telegram Bot</span>
                <span class="tag">Python</span>
                <span class="tag">APIs</span>
              </div>
            </article>
          </a>

